<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Penetrable" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Penetrable,</orth> susceptible, impressible: <cit><quote>his heart granteth no p. entrance to her plaining,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 559" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 559</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p. to your kind entreats,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.225" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 225</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>made of p. stuff,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 36</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>